Film Bharotachea Rajasthanantlea eka lhan ganvant bosoilam,  Tem eka Shanichari nanvanchea ostore voir asa jika tichea paichea mornna uprant tichea avoin soddun dilea. Tichea purea jivitant vaitt noxib disun ieta

== Sonskrutik fattbhuimd ==
Filmachea mathalleak thoddea Rajasthanachea bhagantlo ek dosturecho sondorb asa zoim sokoilea zatichea ostoreank vevsaik rudan korpa khatir bhaddean haddpant ietat je voilea zatichea dadleanchea mornnak vaporpant ietat.Heo ostoreo zankam  "rudali" (roo-dah-lee), utra pormonnem  "ostoreo roddpi " vo ‘roddpi bailo". soglleam samkar kuttumbachem dukh porgottop tanchem kam asta zankam somajik sthanak lagun aplim bhavna porgottunk porvangi nasta..<sup>[3]</sup>

== Kothanok ==
Kanni zomindar/ Thakur (bhattkar zachem patr  Amjad Khan hannem nibhoilam) koddlean suru zata zo Barna (oronneantlo ek ganv) zaka aplea tenklolea mornnachi ani vosthuti, tachim soirim tachea mornnank tache vixim dukh porgottchi nant mhonn zanniv zata.Tea khatir to ek famad rudali zachem nanv Bhikni. (Rakhee) hika,aplea mornna uprant dukh porgottunk sangta. Bhikni vidhva (Dimple Kapadia) hanchea sangaak Thakurachea angnnant ravtat. Tanchi dogainchi ixttagot zata ani Shanichari, Bhiknik aplea jivitachi kanni sangta ji amkam ''flashbacks-''ant pollovnk melltta.

Shanicharicho zolm eka Sonvarak zalolo, zaka vaitt sulusacho dis mantat kiteak tacher Xonicharan  (Saturn) parkhea pormonnem raj korta. Shanicharik sogllem tiche vixim vaitt ghoddtta tea vixim ganvkar tika zapsaldar kortat- zachi survat tichea bapaichea mornnant zali ani tiche avoi Peewli pollun eka lok nattachea pongddant proves kelo. Ozun lhan asun, Shanicharik eka Ganju nanvanchea suranttea kodden kazar kortat zo xevttim eka ganvchea santent mhamarik lagun morunk pavta. Tika palov divpi ekloch ticho put, Budhua (Raghubir Yadav vaddloleachem patr korta),asta zacho ti chodd mog korta.. Punn, taka karonn nastana Peewli kortali toxem heddunk zai.. 

Itlea modekat, Thakuracho cholo  Lakshman Singh (Raj Babbar) ticho mog korta mhonn kollta, ani to tika Thakurachea ''hoveli''nt vavr dita. Ti tachea ibaddlole ghorkan’ni sangata vavurta ani heram modem eksuri asta.. Lakshman, Shanicharik aplea paim-ar ubem ravunk xikovnk ani tiche hok zanna zavnk vavurta ani tichea lagim uloita astana tika “ voir pollovnk” aplea dolleant pollovnk ut’tejon dita Eke rati,  Shanicharchea gavpachea hovelint zalolea dakhovnnent , tika  ek svotachem ghor sangatak don ekor zago asun bhett dita,.

Rokhddoch, vaddlolo Budhua  aple bailek ghora haddtta, Mungri (Sushmita Mukherjee), ek tornnatti xindoll asta ji tachea bhurgeachi avoi zavpachi asa. Punn hi zoddi zhogddot ravtat  ani eka dista ragachea bharar, Mungri tea bhurgeacho gorbhpat korta.. Budhua, raghaborit zavn ghorantlo polltta ani aple avoik eklich soddtta. Tichea koxttank lagun, Shanicharin ken’nach duk gollovnk na oxem kollun ieta

Eke rati,  Shanichari xezarchea ganvant Bhimdatak bhettunk apoitat.  Thakur thoddea vellan morta.. Jen’na Singh aplea paichea mornna uprant. ganv soddunk ievzonn korta ten’na Lakshman Singh ani Shanichari  eka mekak adeus kortat Tankam Bhimdatacho ek sondexkar addaita ani sangta ki Bhiknik mhamaricho tras zala, ani xevttachea kaim minttamni tinnem sanglam ki ti apli avoi Pewli asa, oxi Shanichari hika mhaiti dita.. Shanichari ten’na chodd dukani roddta ani nove rudalicho zago ghevn Thakurchea interak rudan korta<sup>[3][4]</sup>

